    "headline": "BlackRock ETF Adds Ethereum Staking Income To Evolving Valuation Story",
    "summary": "BlackRock (NYSE:BLK) has launched the iShares Staked Ethereum Trust ETF (ETHB), its first spot Ethereum ETF with integrated staking rewards. The product combines direct exposure to Ethereum with on chain staking inside an ETF wrapper. The launch adds to BlackRock's digital asset lineup and introduces a new structure for accessing staking yields through public markets. For a firm best known for its broad fund lineup and role in traditional index investing, ETHB marks an expansion of...",
